1964;;Your Cheatin' Heart;;American;;Gene Nelson;;George Hamilton, Susan Oliver, Red Buttons;;musical, biography;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Your_Cheatin%27_Heart_(film);;A young Hank Williams is trying to earn money by pitching a snake-oil cure-all to the gullible, capping his spiel by picking up his guitar and singing. In the crowd is The Drifting Cowboys, a group of touring country-western musicians who happen to be passing through. They invite Williams to join their group, and music history is made.